  # Simplest ZSH Prompt Configs for Git Branch Name
  
  [![Nick Gibbon](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:32:32/1*g1iF9N_kCVyiJPRQFprlbw.jpeg)](https://medium.com/@njgibbon?source=post_page---byline--3d01602a6f33---------------------------------------)
  
